item.title: Philadelphia Phillies Sign Catcher J.T. Realmuto To Five-Year Contract Worth $115.5 Million

The record is currently held by former Minnesota Twins All-Star Joe Mauer, who signed an eight-year extension worth $184 million in 2010.

Underwood and the One Blue Hill founder “were making out and snuggling together on the lounge chairs by the pool,” an eyewitness exclusively told Us Weekly in September 2021.

item.title: Did Rosie O'Donnell Steal Jerry Seinfeld's Stand-Up Material Long Before He Didn't Cast Her On Seinf
item.description: During Rosie O'Donnell's tenure co-hosting The View, she developed a reputation for not putting up with other people's crap. O'Donnell would notably feud with Donald Trump and have many passionate arguments with her fellow The View co-hosts. Due to O'Donnell's reputation, people often assume the worst of her as proved by the rumors she feuded with Oprah Winfrey. In reality, O'Donnell has many Hollywood friends including Mariah Carey.

item.title: Here's Why Vampire Diaries' Paul Wesley Has Turned To Directing
item.description: The Vampire Diaries ended two years ago, and we're still feeling its loss. The hit CW show, that some of us grew up watching, was a staple in our week, but now it's all over. While most of the cast has moved on, started families, and pursued other roles besides vampires, witches and 1,000 year old originals, one of the cast members never left. You just can't see him. Paul Wesley, who we all loved as the broody Stefan Salvatore on the show, made his directorial debut all the way back in season 5 of The Vampire Diaries.

item.title: The Game Challenges Eminem To Battle, Says 50 Cent "Can't Rap"
item.description: The Game has built a reputation for coaxing rap artists to engage in beef on and off wax throughout his career. Yet, one target he’s yet to lure into a back-and-forth is rap legend Eminem, who has yet to respond to The Game’s challenge to a rap battle following claims that he’s a superior emcee to Em. During an appearance on the Fresh Pair podcast with Katty Customs and Just Blaze, The Game spoke on his reasoning for lashing out at Em, attributing his actions to his competitive spirit rather than a verbal threat.

item.title: Usher To Perform At 2014 MTV Video Music Awards
item.description: Usher will be sliding back to the stage for this year’s MTV Video Music Awards. He joins a line-up of performers that include pop sweetheart Ariana Grande and Australian pop-punk band, 5 Seconds of Summer. “Performing live is the purest form of musical expressing and I am damn happy to return to the VMA stage with new music,” he told MTV in a press release. This will be Ursha’s first VMA performance in three years.

item.description: Ingrid Andress sang the national anthem at the 2024 MLB Home Run Derby — and it was a performance that few will forget. Monday, July 15, brought out all of Major League Baseball’s power hitters, but Home Run Derby winner Teoscar Hernández was hardly the name on everybody’s lips. Andress, 32, is a budding country star who quickly went viral as the spectators at Arlington’s Globe Life Field in Texas were visibly confused by her take on “The Star-Spangled Banner.

item.title: Nicola Yoon (Writer)Bio-Wiki, Age, Husband, Daughter, The Sun Is Also A Star, Books, And Net Worth.
item.description: Nicola Yoon Biography-Wiki Nicola Yoon is a Jamaican-American author. She is well recognized for writing the 2015 young adult novel Everything. Everything is a New York Times bestseller which is the basis of a 2017 film of the same name. Yoon grew up in Jamaica and in Brooklyn, New York. As an undergraduate at Cornell University, she majored in electrical engineering. She was also taking a creative writing class as an elective and it got her hooked on writing.

item.title: Zig Ziglar Net Worth How Much is Zig Ziglar Worth?
item.description: Zig Ziglar, born Hilary Hinton Ziglar on November 6, 1926, was an American author, salesman, and motivational speaker. He had a net worth of $15 million at the time of his death in November 2012. Ziglar is best known for his motivational work, incorporating his Christianity into his messages. He served in the United States Navy during World War II and went on to have a successful career as a salesman, eventually becoming the vice president and training director for the Automotive Performance company.

item.title: 'Big Brother: Over The Top': Where Are The Houseguests Today?
item.description: Of all the seasons of the Big Brother franchise and its spin-offs, not much is spoken of the 2016 one-season version, Big Brother: Over the Top. Also hosted by regular presenter Julie Chen, the ten-episode series is perhaps best remembered for the dramatic hush that fell on the house when she announced that Donald Trump had won the 2016 presidential election.BBOTT - as it is often stylized - was different from the original Big Brother format in that there was a greater focus on live, unedited footage.

item.description: Joan Annabel Spencer was born in Edmonton, Alberta, Canada, on November 16, 1952, to a secretary mother and a World War II pilot father. Through Princess Diana, their family is believed to be connected to the British royal family. Annabel Bowlen is a businesswoman, former teacher, former figure skater, and now philanthropist, but she is most known as the wife of Patrick Dennis “Pat” Bowlen, majority owner of the National Football League’s Denver Broncos.

item.title: Blac Chyna Posts Nude Photo Days Before Giving Birth
item.description: Soon ? A post shared by Blac Chyna (@blacchyna) on Nov 6, 2016 at 5:52pm PST Hot mama! Pregnant Blac Chyna posted a throwback nude photo of herself days before she is set to give birth to her baby girl with fiancé Rob Kardashian. In the sizzling mirror selfie, a completely naked Chyna, 28, shows off her enviable curves and toned abs as she sits in bed, holding her arms over her breasts.

item.title: Blade and Badger Forum List of Blade and Badger Discussions and Forums
item.description: Welcome to the Blade and Badger Forum, where blade enthusiasts and badger lovers come together to share their passion and knowledge. Whether you’re a knife collector, a blade aficionado, or someone who simply appreciates the beauty of badgers, this vibrant community is the perfect place for you. Here, you can engage in discussions, learn from experts, and connect with like-minded individuals who share your enthusiasm for blades and badgers. From tips on knife care and maintenance to discussions on the latest blade and badger-themed events, the Blade and Badger Forum covers a wide range of topics that cater to the diverse interests of its members.

item.title: Craig Conover Is Still With Girlfriend After Ciara Miller Comment
item.description: No split news to report. Southern Charm star Craig Conover revealed that he is still dating girlfriend Natalie Hegnauer amid speculation that he was involved with Summer House’s Ciara Miller. Craig, 32, and Ciara, 25, are set to costar on the upcoming Bravo series Winter House, so fans wondered if something happened between the two during filming after she seemingly flirted with him via Instagram in March. “Well, there’s a lot that happens in Winter House, but no, I’m still with my girlfriend, Natalie, here in Charleston,” he exclusively told Us Weekly on Thursday, April 1.

item.title: Diddys Net Worth Takes A Massive Dip As Brands Refuse To Work With Him After Abuse Allegations
item.description: Highlights Diddy's net worth may plummet amid scandal, with major collaborations drying up in light of disturbing accusations against him. Eyewear deal lost and public backlash ensues after assault footage surfaces; Diddy faces serious allegations under investigation. Diddy denies accusations and is not charged yet; history of legal challenges resurfaces amid new allegations against the rapper. Diddy may be worth an estimated $1 billion, but he could see his net worth dwindle quickly, as his collaborations are beginning to dry up in light of the disturbing accusations against the record producer.

item.title: After Being Sued For $5 Million Over Mixtape Cover, Cardi B Has Announced That She Wins California J
item.description: American rapper and songwriter Cardi B has won a years-long lawsuit regarding the cover art to her 2016 mixtape. Her legal team confirmed that a jury at the Central District of California Court in Santa Ana ruled in the rapper’s favor “on all counts” on Friday (October 21). “I wanna kiss God's feet right now …..IM BEYOND GRATEFUL!!!!” Cardi tweeted after the verdict. The federal jury in Southern California ruled Kevin Michael Brophy did not prove Cardi B misappropriated his likeness.

item.description: Olivia doesn’t just have to answer to The Bachelor ladies! And naturally, Teen Mom OG star Farrah Abraham couldn’t let the comment slide. “Now you can see why it’s offensive of others to judge someone’s parenting drama no matter what age,” Abraham, 24, tells Us Weekly exclusively.

You guys are seeing as much as I’m seeing,” the 28-year-old tennis pro admitted to Us Weekly when asked about Maria’s various feuds in the mansion. “Because every conversation I had with them was one-on-one. I didn’t get to see the group settings. I think that Maria can sometimes be misunderstood.

item.title: Tiffanys Now Serves Breakfast at the Blue Box Caf in NYC
item.description: Fans of Breakfast at Tiffany’s can finally make their dreams come true and enjoy a luxurious meal at Tiffany’s. Tiffany & Co. opened the doors to its new eatery, The Blue Box Café, for its customers on Friday, November 10, on the fourth floor of its flagship store in New York City’s Fifth Avenue. The cafe is the company’s first leap into the retail dining concept, and it will also house their new luxury Home & Accessories collection.

item.title: 'LPBW' Stars Zach, Tori Roloff Reveal Baby Josiah Has Dwarfism
item.description: Zach and Tori Roloff’s newborn son, Josiah, has achondroplasia, the Little People, Big World stars exclusively tell Us Weekly. The couple opened up about their reason for going public with their son’s diagnosis — and why it’s important to remember that his condition is “not his identity.” “He’s Josiah. He has achondroplasia, but he’s not, like, Josiah the achondroplasia,” Zach, 32, tells Us about the couple’s 3-week-old son, who was born on April 30.

Born in rich family foundation, Bryan finished his graduation from the presumed American University in Washington. He procured a degree in Broadcast Communications and was a head of the PSK (Phi Sigma Kappa).

He was inspired by a boxing match between Muhammad Ali and Chuck Wepner. The film was also shot in just 28 days with a small $900,000 budget. Despite working on the film under stressful conditions, it instantly brought Stallone into stardom. The film series led him to more projects that made him the legendary action movie star that he is now.

item.title: Zach Galifianakis Shaves Beard, Debuts Goatee: Picture
item.description: Zach Galifianakis sure doesn't look like he's suffering from a hangover anymore! The 43-year-old actor, who plays Alan in the hit film franchise, debuted a new, sharp look at the Hangover III premiere in Paris on Monday, May 27. Famously known for his trademark scruffy beard, the actor trimmed his hair and sported a mustache with a tame tuft of hair on his chin. He completed his clean-cut style with a three-piece gray suit, a pink shirt and maroon tie.

item.title: All About Kathy Griffins Ex Husband Who Allegedly Stole From Her
item.description: Kathy Griffin started off this crazy 2020 by tying the knot with longtime boyfriend Randy Bick just after midnight on New Year's Eve. It wasn't just a nice New Year kickoff, too. It was a wedding officiated by comedy legend Lily Tomlin. The couple has been inseparable since. There are even rumors that the two might be moving into a smaller home since Griffin recently put her 13,377-square-foot mansion on the market for $16 million. It does sound like a happily married life thing, but it hasn't always been that way for the comedian.

item.title: Anne Hathaway Used Her Real Name For Hollywood, But It Turns Out She Hates It
item.description: Anne Hathaway's career has reached incredible heights incredibly quickly. item.title: Gunna Files Third Bond Motion, Lawyers Cite Lack Of Evidence
item.description: Gunna has been in jail since May 2022 after his YSL label was indicted on 56 different counts, including RICO charges. The rapper, real name Sergio Kitchens, has filed two unsuccessful bond motions, and is now filing a third, as his lawyers believe that the prosecution has provided no evidence that justifies his continued holding. “The State has presented no evidence to support its claims of dangerousness and has dismissed the only serious overt act (75) that was present when the first bond hearing was held,” the 29-year-old’s legal team said within court docs obtained by Complex.

item.title: Who Owns Goodwill? Goodwill Company History
item.description: Goodwill Industries, a renowned nonprofit organization, has a rich history that dates back to its founding in 1902. The company was established by Rev. Edgar J. Helms, a Methodist minister and social innovator, in Boston. Inspired by his desire to alleviate poverty and unemployment, Rev. Helms collected used household goods and clothing from wealthier areas. He then hired individuals who were poor to mend and repair these items, offering them meaningful employment and the opportunity to develop valuable skills.

item.title: Sadie Robertson, Christian Huff Struggled After Welcoming Daughter
item.description: Growing in love. Sadie Robertson got real about how her and husband Christian Huff’s relationship has changed since welcoming their daughter, Honey, in May 2021. “I’ve never felt more strong or confident [in] who I am and in my life,” the 24-year-old former reality star exclusively told Us Weekly while promoting her new book, Who Are You Following? Pursuing Jesus in a Social Media Obsessed World. “Christian and I have never felt closer as a couple just because went through the most vulnerable time ever together.

item.title: When Does Taylor Swift Start Paris Eras Tour in Eastern Time Zone?
item.description: Taylor Swift is getting ready to say bonjour to Paris and kick off the next leg of her Eras Tour in style. Swift, 34, will perform four sold-out shows at Paris’ La Défense Arena starting on Thursday, May 9. The concert will begin at 6:30 p.m. local time with opening act Paramore’s set. The City of Lights is six hours ahead of the United States’ East Coast, meaning that it will be 12:30 p.

item.title: Why Having A Rock Hard Stomach Isn't Always A Sign Of Good Health
item.description: Most of us are striving to be in better shape and get rock hard abs, but having a hard stomach isn't always a sign that all is well. If we aren't one of the lucky few that puts the work in and has that washboard stomach that most of us can only dream of, we all wonder what it really takes to get those abs. For the most part, there are no shortcuts.

item.title: A Mostly Ignored Alanis Morissette Song Detailed Her Split From Ryan Reynolds
item.description: It's been a long time since Ryan Reynolds' name was synonymous with anything other than "Blake Lively's husband." The two have been together since 2011 and tied the knot in 2012. But before Ryan and Blake became couple goals, Reynolds had two other notable relationships. The same year he met Blake, Ryan and Scarlett Johansson both filed for divorce from each other after less than two years of marriage.

item.title: Air Car Shark Tank Founder, Net Worth and Investment
item.description: Have you ever heard of an Air Car? Imagine a vehicle that runs on compressed air, emitting zero pollution and operating on renewable energy. That’s exactly what Zero Pollution Motors aimed to achieve when they appeared on Shark Tank in 2015. Let’s delve into the story of this innovative company, its founders, and what happened after their Shark Tank pitch. Key Takeaways: Zero Pollution Motors appeared on Shark Tank in 2015 with a valuation of $10 million.

item.title: Carolina Dantas: Meet Neymars Ex-Girlfriend And Baby Mama
item.description: Carolina Dantas is a Brazilian social media personality. She was born on October 21st, 1993, in Sao Paulo, Brazil. Although she kissed fame when she started her liaison with the Brazilian footballer Neymar Jr, she has gained a large fan following of her own now. The star presently has over 2.6 million followers on Instagram, giving her a pretty influential ground on the global network. Carolina graduated from Colegio Adventista de Santos in the year 2011.
